$interpreted: Anxious Bewitcher: Pearl Palace has been found out? What are we gonna do!?
Scared Bewitcher: Just wait here 'til we're taken away? Killed!?
Soohyeon: I'm so sorry... I'm so sorry... this is all my fault...
Li Hwa: No, this could have happened even if I were here.
Li Hwa: It doesn't matter at this point. We should just worry about getting out of here.
Soohyeon: Getting out of here? Where are we gonna go!?
Li Hwa: Everyone's coming back with me to Seamoon Manor. Quick, everyone get their things!
Li Hwa: Meong Sa, help me clean up here.
Li Hwa: If I lose my research, all these years of work will have been for nothing... Plus, it'll be used as evidence!
Soohyeon: Let me help, too!
Li Hwa: No, no, you've helped enough, Soohyeon.

Li Hwa: I've already asked so much of you... 
Please, leave while you still can!
Soohyeon: But... we're a team, Li Hwa! You've always said that! I can't leave if I know you need help!
Li Hwa: But... you've worked so hard hiding your identity up to this point... If you're found out...
Soohyeon: It doesn't matter right now! There's no time to think about what-ifs!
Meong Sa: Li Hwa, Soohyeon... I have an idea.
Li Hwa: An idea? What?
Meong Sa: ...It might buy you both some time.
Weak Seahorse: Just up ahead, I swear! I saw two bewitchers!!
Tough Guard: Hmph... Hope you're not just making stuff up for the reward money.
Weak Seahorse: (I'm scared, but... if this money means I can bring my child to the hospital, then...)
Meong Sa: Everyone stay away!!
Mean Guard: What the...!?
Soohyeon: Help me! Heeelp!!!
Mean Guard: Isn't that Soohyeon's voice!?
Tough Guard: Soohyeon, what are you doing out dressed like that!?
Soohyeon: I... I want to buy something to surprise mom, but... she doesn't let me go out, so I had to disguise myself...
Soohyeon: I never thought this would... ah, I'm so scared!
Meong Sa: Sh-Shut up!! Or I'll... I'll...
Tough Guard: Let go of Miss Soohyeon, bewitcher scum!
Mean Guard: Quick, go report this. We'll stay here!
Meong Sa: Take one step closer and I'll kill her! Or... Or maybe I'll bewitch her!!
Mean Guard: She's the arbiter's daughter, damnit!!
Tough Guard: What are we supposed to do!?
Mean Guard: How should I know? This is the first time this sort of thing has happened...!
Soohyeon: (I really hope this whole thing doesn't go haywire... I just wanted to give Li Hwa some more time!)
Soohyeon: Watch out! Behind you!!
Crazed Guard: My hands... how...
Crazed Guard: Ah... guhh...
Crazed Guard: Gyaaahh!!!
Mean Guard: Help... Help me...!!
Weak Seahorse: Don't come any closer!!
Meong Sa: Get off!!
Soohyeon: Watch out!
Weak Seahorse: Stay away... Just get away from us...
Soohyeon: It's... It's okay...
Weak Seahorse: So you're working together!? You... you want to bewitch us, don't you!?
Weak Seahorse: Monster!! You deserve to die!
Meong Sa: That's enough! Can you really not recognize me!?
Soohyeon: Meong Sa, you know him?
Weak Seahorse: ...Meong Sa? You said... her name is Meong Sa!?
Meong Sa: ......
Weak Seahorse: No way! That's impossible! That's... my wife's name...
Weak Seahorse: How could my wife have turned into one of those monsters...
Soohyeon: Meong Sa... you always wanted to go home to see your husband...
Meong Sa: When I realized I had become a bewitcher, I snuck out and ran away from home... to protect them...
Meong Sa: I had nowhere to go. I was just outside, trying to survive, until Li Hwa found me.
Meong Sa: Li Hwa took me in... took in all of us bewitchers with nowhere to go. And now you sell us all out to the guards!?
Weak Seahorse: I... I didn't know...
Weak Seahorse: You were one of them all along...
Meong Sa: My child...!
Weak Seahorse: I thought you left me... you didn't love me anymore...
Weak Seahorse: Our child is sick, and I needed money for the doctor... That's the only reason I reported you...
Weak Seahorse: I'm sorry, Meong Sa! I'm so sorry!
Meong Sa: ......
Soohyeon: No... it's no one's fault...
Alliance Guard: Quick, the bewitcher is just ahead!
Weak Seahorse: I'm sorry... this is all my fault. Let me take responsibility!
Weak Seahorse: I'll distract the guards!
Weak Seahorse: Please, take care of my wife and child, Miss Soohyeon!
Meong Sa: Wait—
Soohyeon: Meong Sa, there's no time! Let's get somewhere safe!
